Article of it gazdaság
This year also increased by an average of 16% in the commercial triangle of gold the the usual Christmas of the newspaper, but in all the supermarkets a growth was registered over the thousand huf.
As in December of last year had already gone off "," the prices in the food supermarkets, thus not experienced a drastic increase in comparison with the high point of departure.
However, clearly it is terrifying to consumers the fact that what the last year could buy at a price below the nine thousand huf, at the present time they can do neither by ten thousand.
The basket of it in the supermarkets studied with a minimum of 91 exceeded the psychological limit of ten thousand huf.
And the highest value was 10 573 huf.
(in the year 2003 this basket cost 6800 huf.)
