Comparing the values of the most expensive of last year with the of the most quarter of this year, the difference has been a 12%, while the growth between the cheapest of last year and the more expensive of this year has been a 21%.
The average growth was 1480 huf.
Last year the average growth of the prices was of 1206 huf, so that during the Christmas of last year in the prices felt the increase of VAT.
Precisely this process was which destroyed the trade, the supermarkets visibly were unable to take a decision on the margin of prices to apply for each product and to assess the effect of a change of the prices on consumption.
If the retailer plans badly the speed of the circulation of a product, can lose an important benefit in the margin that conforms to the volume of sales.)
The increase in the price of the basket of it reached such ends as a result of the increase of the VAT, the more expensive was over with 1720 huf to value registered in 2006, whereas in the cheapest the difference was only 844 huf.
This year is not produced such extremes, since the highest price of has now been 1630 than last year, and the cheapest also increased with 1284 huf.
Comparing the two seasons, a catastrophic growth registered in the prices in less than 20 months, in the supermarkets grew by more than 30% of the price of the consumer goods from the first necessity.
- but this does not necessarily confirms the numbers of the Central Bureau of Statistics: this office, in the case of some staple foods registered in the interval of 12 months an increase of price over the 30 per cent.
Thus, for example, in addition to the wheat, also in the case of the egg.)
According to the basket of it, in the latter case it seems almost impossible, because in the price of the product that was already quite expensive last year in comparison to the base, it is recorded in the worst cases as soon as a 10% increase in prices.
According to all the indices, the suppliers of feed have a stronger position than the egg, being able to impose the drastic increase in the prices to the multinationals.
The supermarkets do not complain in the commercial triangle of gold, talk constantly about positive results.
According to our experiences collected, the majority of consumers of the three visited shops, because they are not interested in the prices.
Of all the products they buy large quantities, taking the food for palettes preserved.
