400 million euros more for infrastructures
The Hungarian Minister of Finance veres and the Vice-President of the European Investment Bank (EIB) Marta gajecka signed on Friday in Budapest three of the credit for a total value of 400 million euros to finance infrastructure, education, transport and the environment, as well as of the energy sector.
The European Investment Bank (EIB) approved in 2006 a budget of 300 million euros for finance in the Hungarian budget to the projects in transport and environmental protection, which will be carried out of the subsidy of the funds of cohesion, of which the parties had already previously signed a contract of credit for a value of 100 million, the contract that have signed it refers to the use of the remaining 200 million euros.
The contract of the credit of 150 million euros are also destined to finance the budget of the educational projects.
The EIB approved in total 300 million euros for this objective of Hungary, on the use of the remaining 150 billion euros, the decision will be taken later, to extend the contract of credit.
The parties signed a contract for 50 million euros for innovations, that the budget will mainly to the project of innovations and research of the University of debrecen.
During the talks also included the subject of the construction of the 4th metro line.
It came to the agreement that when Hungary completed with the EU, the details of the financing of the metro, they will treat the subject that whether or not it is necessary to modify the original contract and how to do it.
According to veres, this will be able to take place to earlier in the first quarter of 2008.
Since 1990, the EIB financed in total 113 projects in Hungary, at the price of a billion euros.
The interest of the credits are adjusted to the Euribor and the EIB provides a grace period of eight years, without receiving Commission for supporting the credit at the disposal of the debtor.
Bulgaria, the real property of the EU
It is admirable the development of the Bulgarian property market - the attention of all of Europe is directed towards this Balkan country before little mentioned.
What thing, where in the market and those who buy cheaper for the EU, which is recommended quickly?
Analysis of the Bulgarian of d / Max.
The preferred target for the property acquisitions in Eastern Europe is without doubt Bulgaria, with their cheap apartments of the ski runs and the of the beaches.
The regions of bansko, borovec, pamprovo and vitosa are the most preferred, while in the beaches albena, the "golden coast", the "Costa del Sol," the old sozopol and nesebar, but more and more people look for buildings in the vicinity of kavarna and balchik.
According to the analysts of d / Max in Bulgaria, sooner or later, too, the central area of the country - as veliko tarnovo, gabrovo, Elena, triavna - will wake up the interest of the property developers and more and more people to buy buildings in the area especially cheap rus.
In the same way it will be able to be attractive capital Sofia, the commercial spaces and offices promise a rapid recovery of investment.
Bulgaria is the best way to become one of the most attractive paradise of course of Europe, being able to be so an outstanding destiny for the other two stations, in addition to the summer and winter.
Therefore, the cautious investors are already doing their purchases, for example in the vicinity of bansko.
In view of the analysts, to purchase buildings in Bulgaria, also make an effort to change their life and their way of living.
The majority of the clients are British, but they also come from France, Belgium, Spain and increasingly of Romania.
Likewise the Maltese and Cypriot developers are present and traditionally there are many Russian clients on the beaches of the Black Sea and the paradise of skiing.
The foreign customers can be classified into three groups - Georgi jankov says, regional director of d / Max in Bulgaria.
Those who try to settle here they buy new buildings or renewed for a price between 50 and 100 thousand euros or old houses in bad shape between 5 and 15 thousand euros, so soon.
They require good communication and access to them is important, in addition to the proximity of a big city, shops and generally of a local doctor.
They constitute the second category the buyers of category (Bulgaria in December was included among the first 10 holiday destinations of the Germans).
They constitute the third group the property investors who do their shopping, with the hope of benefit to medium or long term.
The price of the properties goes in constant growth, since the demand is increasing.
Although in the European Union, Bulgaria has the lowest real estate prices, in the last five years these suffered an annual increase of 21%
The increase in the price of the buildings considerably surpasses the growth of wages.
Fodor and the six hundred Hungarians
As reported to the Minister of the environment and hydrology fodor the meetings of experts will end on Tuesday and Wednesday after the official inauguration will continue the negotiations at the level of ministers on the international climate regime after 2012.
The experts and politicians from 192 countries of the world to deliberate on the road map of balí that has on the efforts after the period of reduction of emissions, established in the Kyoto Protocol, effective until 2012.
At the present time are carried out lively discussions on the individual among the developing countries and the industrialized.
The United States has already indicated that at the moment does not want to negotiate on the precise numbers, although it tends to come to the agreement that in comparison with the situation of 1990, until the year 2020 decreases with 25 to a 40% the emission of gases responsible for the greenhouse effect.
Another great issue of the Conference is that if the industrialized countries, in addition to reduce emissions, or are not willing to provide material and technological to the countries that need it.
It came to an agreement on the also helps to offer to the developing countries.
The background of support, foreseen in the Kyoto Protocol, it will be led by a board of management integrated by 16 members, probably in the global fund for the environment of the UNO (gef) - written "piac és profit."
The six by hundreds of Hungary
In the name of Hungary, the Minister of the environment and hydrology fodor supports the efforts of the EU to maintain its leading role in the global protection of the climate and to promote the signing of the new international agreement until 2009.
The Minister said that the EU is committed to reduce until 2020, with regard to the level of 1990 in 20% of its emissions of gas, responsible for the greenhouse effect, regardless of whether or not the "agreement signed after 2012" and is ready to engage in decreasing even 30% if the other great developed regions of the world, and the developing countries are also ready to assume commitments in accordance with its responsibility and its capacities.
Fodor noted that the signatory countries of the Kyoto Protocol of 1997 committed themselves to decrease in a 5.2%, within this then the 15 Member States of the EU are committed in fulfilling an 8% reduction.
The commitment of Hungary is decreasing with 6% of the emission of gases responsible for the greenhouse effect with regard to the period between 1985 and 87, that our country will comply with - it indicates the press release of the Ministry of Environment.
It is very much what is at stake in balí, since that within two years it will be necessary to sign the international agreement of the climatic policy in the long term, because if it does not, it is certain that its entry into force was postponed for after 2012; in this case the reduction commitments, assumed in the Kyoto Protocol does not be followed immediately by a new international system of reduction of emissions, whose need was notified in its most recent report by the IPCC, international scientific association of the UN that deals with climate change, which received the Nobel Peace Prize.
With that, the reduction of emissions would suffer a delay, and they will not be able to prevent an increase of more than O C of the average temperature of the earth, the fact that according to the scientists have immeasurable consequences and irreversible.
The British army recruit in youtube
The units of the British army in a distributor of videos publish published on actions filmed in Iraq and Afghanistan to popularize themselves.
The first British air force () was the one that took advantage of the services of youtube: the special units displaced persons in Afghanistan since the March 2006 are charging videos on its actions against the Taliban - the BBC reported.
These recordings made with mini mounted cameras on the helmets is controlled in the general body of operations of Kandahar, then they are sent to London to be loaded on the Internet.
The political message is unavoidable
They are already 139 recordings originating from the soldiers of the air force that has been borne in this way to the Internet and its "channel" has already been seen by more than 75 billion people.
The British Ministry of Defence is registered in the spring of 2007, under the name of "defence headquarters" and videos of both actions perpetrated in Iraq and Afghanistan, while the department of the Community of Nations British Commonwealth Office) (as the multinational forces in Iraq - mnfi) have its own channel.
Operation in Afghanistan
Originally the air force had loaded the videos with recruitment objectives, but in view of the Ministry of Defence serve also to present to the public the true objective of the presence of the British army abroad.
This type of advertising practically does not cost anything in comparison with the conventional television spots of recruiting - the expert declared the BBC in defence Gordon - however, inevitably have some political message, because in a specific way justifies the reason being the military action decided by the government.
The Americans prepared a video game
The army also worries about the fact that, in addition to the recordings and censured, in the distributor also keen videos appear, for example on the death of the soldiers: in "the official" films of propaganda, a little hypocritical, the officials talk as a maximum of leaks, without presenting however the bloody part of the battles.
In addition, in the fields of battle of Iraq and Afghanistan have borne the Internet because numerous videos recorded in real operations, but the British army alone ultimately is taking advantage of this opportunity.
The Americans use a form a little different for the recruitment to the free video games of shots called America 's army, in that in the middle of a more or less real situation the player cannot be put directly in place of the soldiers.
