They are met the forces of the giant strike
The trade unions of League and the National Federation of working commissions will constitute the Friday a strike Commission to coordinate the strike on Monday that will last indefinitely.
On Saturday will be held a meeting of protest, while that on Monday - day in that it will hold the final vote on the law of public health - will begin work.
With any certainty this action will cause great difficulties in the transport, since that will stop completely the railway traffic and until 1 p.m. there will be on strike, also to the workers of the company of collective transport of Budapest.
On Friday evening the unions of League will report on the details of their strike on Monday to celebrate together with the National Federation of working commissions.
Likewise the Commission strike of the League and the National Union of train drivers' which will coordinate the actions of Monday.
On Saturday will be held a meeting of protest, while that on Monday the unions participants will be on strike indefinitely, if it does not come to an agreement with the government.
This means that - in the day of the parliamentary vote on the law of public health - do not report on the date of the end of the strike begun.
If the national assembly disapproves of the law of public health, the trade unions will withdraw its call to strike.
However, if the law is approved, will meet the strike commissions and will decide on the future.
On the basis of the order of the day of the Monday of the National Assembly, it is also possible that only vote itself above the law of public health in the hours very entered at night, or maybe next to the midnight.
As a result of the strike that will begin on Monday, it will be necessary to include significant difficulties in the transport: in the railways will be employed indefinitely, in the morning can to stop a part of the collective transport of Budapest, and more than half of the inter-city transport of buses of the volán.
Simultaneously, in numerous points of the country will be closing of half of the ways of the roads.
Numerous trade unions and civil organizations have adhered to strike, their names are constantly update on the web page of the league.
Some trade unions announced its strike indefinitely, others by definite time.
Until Thursday evening the railroad state and the free trade union of railway workers (sltf) could not come to an agreement or even on the essential services, though, at the coming near Christmas festivities, every time there are more people who travel on the trains.
According to information received up to now, since the start of the day until 1 p.m. there will be on strike, the workers of the company of collective transport of Budapest, those of Budapest airport from 7 to 9 o'clock in the morning, will celebrate a strike of four hours, the trade unions of the League of the electrical industry and of thermal energy, the trade unions of the educators called a strike of 2 and the democratic Union of educators of 2 to 8 hours.
The Hungarian Association of doctors are pronounced in national strike in alternative schedules and democratic Union of the workers of the sector of the health and social (sdtsss) that are part of the forum of Union cooperation, will celebrate a strike of two hours.
The most important of the four demands formulated by the League is that the government to withdraw its proposal relating to the reform of the public health and submit a new vision to a social debate.
The second demand is to gradually introduce the new form of calculation of pensions which will come into force next year.
The third is that they guarantee, even before 2010, in the case of the anticipated pensions to the possibility of the occupations that deserve it can enter the system.
The fourth reason of the strike is that the free trade union of railway workers (sltf) that is part of the trade unions of league, not to accept the proposal of the Ministry of Economy and railway transport on the sidelines and wait for another different proposal.
Political capital: in the country increases the risk for the guard
According to the division of analysis of risks (risk analysing division) of the political capital to the activity of the guard, constituted in August of this year, with the support of the movement for a Hungary, from various points of view has increased the political risk of Hungary and of the region.
In the "warning on risks" of the written: in relation to the activity of the guard the major political risk constitutes the fact that "with the worsening of the existing ethnic tensions among the population, Gypsy and gypsy of Hungary, even in the short term to be able to take place ethnic violent clashes."
The main reason for this is that the political strategy of the guard is probably the provocation of an event of this character - the representative of the Institute of research.
They stated that everything that is due to one of the main lack of the protagonists of the Hungarian political life: "the protagonists of the public life handed over the public debate of gypsy problem to the representatives of the political groups, radical extremists, who could support his political strategy on the existing discrepancies between gypsies and Hungarians."
This aggravates the problem, makes the dialogue, strengthens the extremists and increases the likelihood of the outbreak of the violent conflicts - estimates.
In addition to that, according to the Institute of research, the activity of the national guard, by consequence of the great attention to the average national and international, "deteriorated significantly the image of Hungary abroad, especially when it comes to the stability and the democratic development of the country.
We recall that: from the autumn of 2006 received ever greater publicity and boost the reorganization of the radical groups and the extreme right of Hungary, and that since the summer of 2007 have constituted in the country that numerous organizations themselves of "associations of national".
"The common feature of these groups is that as civil organizations, while openly proclaim the training of its Members for the defence - even armed - (civil defence, it proposes, defender of public order), referring to the ineptitudes of the police, the army, that is to say of the State" - add.
They stated: all it takes place in accordance with the method which tries to give him a civil presentation to different political aspirations, based on the dissatisfaction of the company with the policy and the political parties.
Therefore emphasize the civil and the form of partnership in the case of these associations not only serve to prevent the legal problems of the legal inscription, but it is at the same time also a political strategy.
According to the analysis, the activity of the guard is a risk factor also from the point of view of the vicinity relations.
"in recent months, in numerous States they referred to the guard as a potential danger, whereas the political figures of certain countries, they want to justify its own policy with the creation of the Hungarian guard.
All this influences the political stability of the region "- they added.
According to the Institute of research, the Constitution of the guard is not an isolated phenomenon in Central and Eastern Europe, so that in the whole region is increased the political risks.
They wrote that the guard works in such a way that, for example, the Bulgarian, whose constitution was announced in the month of August 2007 for the Bulgarian National Union (unb) of the extreme right.
The Constitution of the Bulgarian guard due to the massive disturbances of gypsies that took place in one of the quarters of Sofia (krasna poliana).
Taking advantage of this situation, the unb decided to constitute the custody, with the argument that the objective of the organization is "national".
In its opinion, in the last 17 years were "gypsy terror" in Bulgaria, nevertheless the State remained impotent and indifferent to the facts - recalls the political capital.
They added: this initiative has caused an animated discussion in the Bulgarian public opinion.
Just as it is written, indicates the increase of the risk of the ethnic confrontations that certain organizations gypsies of Bulgaria have announced that to resist, constitute its own guard.
As the functioning of the guard has so far shown similarities with the of the Bulgarian, it cannot be excluded that also gypsies of Hungary will react to the threat in a similar way, organizing its own self - can be read in the warning about the risks of political capital.
The Director of investigations of political capital, Attila juhász to the question of the news agency stated: the analysis of risks is one of the activities of the Institute of research.
As he said, every year publish its analysis of risks and when they experience something that can influence the change of risk, inform the public opinion, as happened in this case, publishing its warning about the risks.
The party does not always written with red numbers
In Hungary, the law defines precisely the days that is written with red numbers in the timetable, and it has already become a widespread practice that concerning the festival - that next year there will be less - the working days.
Even in the EU or in North America are unitary.
The Hungarian laws make a difference between national holiday, celebration of the state and festive days.
The festive days fundamentally related to religious holidays and historic events.
We celebrate the new year also: the last day of the old, as well as the first day of the new year is festive - the latter above all so that they can rest that happened celebrating the year old.
Throughout the year we have eleven holidays written with red numbers in the calendar.
It is a national holiday on 15 March in memory of the 1848 revolution and 23 October, commemorative day of the revolution of 1956.
On 20 August we celebrated the founding of the State, the 1st of May the celebration of the work, the 1st and 2nd of November we remember our family and friends dead.
In addition, in our country are celebrations of two days Easter, the Pentecost and Christmas.
According to the timetable, our state, national or religious seldom coincide with a weekend, for that is often makes bridge when before or after the holiday there is only one working day.
In exchange for the purposes of like that, during the previous Saturdays cannot stay away of work or the school.
Is the Minister of work that regulates in its specific decree when it is necessary to work exactly to change the directly preceding or after the festival.
This legal norm compliance is obligatory for all the owners and their employees, as well as for the employees and civil servants.
It is not obligatory in exchange for the companies and institutions of services that, due to its function, work uninterruptedly even during the festive days.
This year the order of work will be able to be altered only around the celebrations of the end of year: from 24 December virtually stops the life in the country, since according to the experiences, the majority of the people "bridge" during the days between the Christmas and the end of the year or take their holidays during these days.
The next several of our holidays will coincide with the middle or with the end of the week, so that there will be fewer changes in the working days that this year.
First, the agenda will be modified concerning the celebration of the work so that soon, for four successive days, the workers can rest.
On Saturday, 26 April will be working day, for that to change the Friday, 2 may be festive day.
Another change is related to the celebration of 23 October: on Saturday 18 October, it will be necessary to work instead of Friday 24.
On the other hand, the year that comes under the celebration of the end of the year will be able to rest, since from 24 December does not work in almost anywhere, even though the last day of the year is a Wednesday.
Six deterrent to turn the life of your colleagues
E-mails that we forget to send, sound messages that never receive, innocent lies that happen without realizing: they all form part of our daily folklore "in the work.
It is necessary to decide whether you yourself to the bother you or the confused situations that can to others.
Advice.
$isculpa, forgot to warn you that have sought from the Department of marketing "- one of your colleagues.
That therefore does not go to an appointment?
Ideally feels it and try to repair the matter, calls the marketing department to tell them that they forgot to deliver the message - this is the solution less habitual).
In the majority of the times the matter is resolved requesting excuses.
Before proceeding to explanations, it is worthwhile pondering on things with which you can spoil the life of your colleagues and to avoid them.
You take something that is not yours?
There is no more irritating thing that when you want to take a document, a tool of office or your telephone and do not find them.
You that yesterday the stapler placed on the table, but for this morning disappeared?
Will you find your Pen lost in the table of one of your colleagues?
Do not take anything to your colleagues without asking them to, because with reason they get them to remove its things.
Do not envelopes or post-it the Bureau, because it will be able to be unpleasant when you need them immediately and exhausted before the time.
You gossip about the private life of your colleagues?
There is no good solution to stop rumours that are already running.
Who, what it is doing and with whom?
Where does and why?
Do not spend around the world, the information (guesswork) that you have on the private life of your colleagues!
Do not abuse the confidence of your colleague, when he shares its most intimate secrets with you!
Buries in yourself what you have heard and not gossip about your colleague in his absence, although it also others know the things it.
You go to leave for disease?
When you call for telephone the office and say that you are ill and you hurt unbearably the head, feel badly or, feel that this day resting; think that others should do your work, your tasks, your work for term.
You did not bother to your colleague!
If you know in advance that the following day will not go to the Bureau, or it will be able to something, for which you have to stay at home, them, so that your colleagues or your head do not have confronted with you lack the following day.
Tarareos, laughs, telephone calls
You are put in your work, but they do sudden him the risillas of your colleagues?
You have heard involuntarily a telephone conversation that it would have been better not to listen to it?
Do not bother to your colleagues with your tarareos, songs, talks aloud (less when you do over his head), protests, constant, expressing your discontent aloud.
All of these can be uncomfortable, even if they are not in depth at this moment in a project (writing, planning, organization).
Do they blame others for a mistake?
You do not blame others if you have not finished in time something, you have forgotten to send a letter or an important message!
Do not refer to the chaos eventually prevailing in the Bureau, nor to the noise that make your colleagues!
You must recognize if you have made a mistake that harms other and must repair the mistake!
Ask how you can restore your lack!
Do you feel too at home in the office?
Jogging and: habit very convenient for the House, but it is not suitable for the office!
You are not seen a comfortable although your occupation allows!
You are not, respects to your colleagues, and to yourself dressing daily, elegant and clothes when your occupation therefore requires!
