600 thousand people do not manage to change their driving licence
To six hundred thousand drivers they happened to date, and for that reason does not manage to change its old driving licence whose validity ends at the end of the year.
Today is the last day when people can ask for the change to the officials them time until the end of the year in expressing the new card.
However, the department not fear that after the new year is found along the road hundreds of thousands of drivers without the valid card.
According to traffic, the card has not changed mainly those who do not even want to conduct.
Whereas in the towns announce a rapid reduction of the change of cards, the offices of the metropolis full of applications and the interest for the new card has increased.
The town hall calculated around 2 daily customers.
In the lines are waiting half an hour.
In Prague, they have still not taken by the new card around yet drivers.
The emission of a new card hard twenty days.
However, it is possible to ask for the discharge of the card in the shorter space of five days.
But in this case the driver must pay for five hundred crowns.
The drivers who obligatorily must change its card and does not reach until the end of the year, but will go out to the roads without the valid card will risk to a fine as of January.
The offender will pay a maximum of two thousand crowns.
The police can arrange the breach with a reprimand.
In the event of a breach breach the fine will rise to 2,500 crowns.
According to the information before it could receive a fine that person who does not go anywhere.
They would be able to pay likely to 30,000 crowns.
The department appealed to the offices for fines of a crown, as most.
According to the director of the Department of Transportation, Karel hanzelka, the fines billion Crowns threaten anybody.
According to him, the driving licence is a document in which people can decide whether they want to or not.
It is not the identity card that each person must have valid.
The people who do not want to conduct should deliver the driving licence.
