Cuba, the most beautiful island of the Caribbean
For the vistantes is really the island of freedom.
Anything that expect of their holidays may come to comply, provided that choosing correctly.
Beaches and golden, large waves or a calm sea as a pond.
The palm trees and all including with waiters offering pizzas on the beach, frozen or various cocteles.
Kitesurfing, Golf and roulette.
In the island of the Caribbean Sea can find all this and much more.
Only in an island is still much more and that island is Cuba, the greatest and most beautiful of all the islands of the great Antilles.
At the time of the Spanish, Cuba became the bastion of the conquest of America.
Columbus called it, the most beautiful place that human eye has seen.
The Havana became store and port of burden of the treasures that the Spanish extracted from America and led to Europe.
And then came the American period.
The national hotel grew at the end of the year 20.
It was ordered to build one of the leaders of the American mafia, Lucky Luciano, because everything that there was of criminality in the USA (and therefore, prohibited) was welcomed and supported in Cuba as drugs, game and prostitution.
Among its guests were, among other
Winston Churchill, ava Gardner, Frank Sinatra.
In Havana high buildings rose, by wide avenues ran the cars that were a symbol of worship in 50 years of the last century.
Ernest Hemingway bought a property in San Francisco Paula, next to Havana, and in cojimar had its yacht.
In the walls of the bodeguita of the left their companies the stars of the world of spectacle and politicians of all America.
And today?
In the walls of the bodeguita habanense you can also leave their autograph.
In the bar of expensive national hotel the cocktail according to their wishes.
And these cars already of worship of the fifties, until today continue working for the Havana, because those lada and Fiat that were already some time ago have rusted between these humid and salty winds.
Even though the Havana, especially the old is deteriorating dramatically, does not exist in the vicinity so many wonderful monuments as there.
Elsewhere in beauty, for example, Trinidad.
Due to the fact that tourism brings so much money necessary, its development is guaranteed.
In the last fifteen years, new hotels, not only in Havana, but also in the dock, at the expense of the province of holguín and in small islands as key, key Guillermo and others.
Cuba still offers a curiosity that is unique in the world, and that is highly valued by the lovers of rail.
The sugar cane is transported from the vast plantations to the sugar factories for narrow in steam engines or electrical.
Its garages for dozens of years not discovered and now they are there, machines that work and whose models brothers in other parts of the world, only to be found in museums.
Where to go?
The more known to the majority of the vistantes does not change.
And for that reason, it is not necessary to speak more of the Havana dry.
Perhaps, only to remember that in the already mentioned property of Hemingway there is a museum that for those who are lovers of the writer, must not leave to visit it.
The valley of vineyards is the most corner of Cuba to the west of the island.
Exuberant vegetation which grows on grounds of rock.
Heaps, rock and rocks of raised the falls in the valley, and in its caves is fertile land, thanks to which it formed which hide dense vegetation.
The valley is the place where they are cultivated, probably, the tobacco of greater quality in Cuba.
Visiting some of the factories of pure can meet its final product.
Perhaps someone seem interesting that there was rolled the Chilean part of the series, the major Zeman.
Trinity
City of old ancestry was founded not long after the Spanish colonizing the island.
Slavery and the sugar brought fame and wealth.
The wealth became beauty with the construction in the small town.
The Spanish colonial architecture, especially influenced by the French colonists come later, in four centuries has hardly changed.
Trinity, between the sea and the mountain range of escambray, is such a remote place that still in 50 years of the last century was not road that joined with the rest of the country.
Such isolation helped to remain outside the rest.
Nothing new is built, and for that reason, either, nothing was destroyed, for every person was happy to have where they live.
If you have more time to be in trinity that a single late, it is worthwhile to know interesting places in the nearby surroundings as the beach of ancón or the valley of the sugar factories.
The night belongs to the House of music, which encourages with its music the silence of the mornings.
Baracoa
Small town in the west of Cuba, some regard as the most beautiful of the island.
Surely this is already confirmed by the proper way.
The two roads that arrive there from Guantánamo should pass by discharges and mountains, as well as for a nature that hardly knows the action of the man.
This Eastern place of Cuba has been recorded as world heritage by UNESCO thanks to its intact nature.
There do the best chocolate, in his church have the Cross of Columbus - in fact it is a cross that came 100 years later the landing) and since the hill, where was the House and that there is now a hotel with the same name, can see the mountains, and among them, the most well-known, the anvil.
