The Congress approved the transposition of the MiFID, which came into force on 1 November
In parallel to its parliamentary procedure, which finally today with the vote on the part of the Congress of the amendments incorporated into the project in the Senate, the government has submitted at the public hearing the regulation that will develop the new law, with the objective of that they both enter into force before the end of the year.
The representatives of the different groups agreed in highlighting the effort made by representatives and Senators to negotiate and agree on the better regulation for the sake of guaranteeing the protection of investors and regulating the activity of the entities with detail so that the markets function efficiently.
The MiFID, that modifies the law of the stock market, means the modernization of the financial markets, which reinforces the protection to the investor, improves the powers of the national Commission of the stock market (cnmv) and promotes cooperation between the different supervisors of the European Union.
The new regulation will allow services of financial advice both to companies specialized as to natural or legal persons and creates a new type of signatures of financial services (esis), the societies of financial advice (afi), which will join the societies of values, the agencies and the administrative management of portfolio.
In addition, it extends the number of systems for the execution of operations on financial instruments, so that the secondary market regulated they join the multilateral systems of negotiation and the orders internalization systems, which will compete with the current managers of market.
The law also obliges the investment companies to divulge information in the market on the key aspects of its profile of business, exposure to risk and forms of risk management and requires them to lead a record of all the operations which they carry out, to facilitate the monitoring on the part of the cnmv.
In its step by the Commission of the economy of the Congress, incorporated a number of modifications, among which emphasizes that the debts are considered as a financial instrument "complex" given its high danger to the investor, that has been demonstrated with what happened with the debt of American mortgages of high risk (subprime).
In addition, it took advantage of the transposition of the directive for legally delimit the functions which can develop the graduates in economic and commercial 30 years after that in 1977 was approved the Royal Decree that delimits the professional functions reserved economists.
For its part, the Senate incorporated the creation of new figures in the financial sector, such as that of the mediator, who worked for someone else, they do not need access to the cnmv and will be able to give his services of the marketing of products and collection of customers to different companies of investment.
The IPC harmonized increases five tenth in November, until the 4.1%
This indicator, which serves to Eurostat to incorporate it into the calculation of the rate of inflation in the European Union, provides an advance of how the prices in Spain during the month of November.
Its publication responds to the policy of Eurostat and the European Central Bank (ECB) to provide data on time and quality to the produced in the United States.
The anticipated indicator is calculated using the same procedure that the employee for the consumer price index harmonized, but using different methods of statistics to consider the information that is not arranged at the time of its publication.
The ine recalled that the information that it provides the anticipated indicator is only reference, for that is not necessarily coincide with the final data, which will be introduced next 14 December.
"The IPC will continue in relatively high levels"
The second Vice-President and Minister of Economics, Pedro Solbes, has stated that the increase in a 4.1% of the IPC in November, is a "temporary", but at the same time have foreseen that the price index will continue in relatively high "" levels in the next few months.
In any case Solbes has pointed out in the corridors of the Congress that "if the figure is not good" the differential of inflation of Spain with regard to monetary union remains "more or less the same of recent years.
It has also explained that in November "has been less surprise that in the previous month, when the government does not include such a high increase.
"We expected a figure about 4%", has admitted to the Minister of Economics with regard to the data advanced today.
