What I need insurance?
The car insurance, which covers the driver in the face of possible accidents, means an important cost that will depend on various factors such as age, sex, seniority of the card, the marital status, the type of vehicle to ensure that the use of this one, among others.
The car is only the beginning.
And the fact is that, to choose the right of car insurance is even more difficult to choose the vehicle model.
In the first place, there is to be clear about what we are talking about.
The car insurance is an agreement between an insurance company and the insured.
This commitment is materialized in a contract of insurance, which establishes that the company receives the value of the premium agreed to change that hold responsible for the obligation to pay compensation in the event of accident.
The premium is the price of insurance, which is established taking into account various factors such as age, sex, seniority of the card, the marital status, the type of vehicle to ensure that the use that him this, among others.
The insurance companies establish their prices according to the statistics, so that more likely to have an accident, greater quota to pay.
It is for this reason that both the biggest of 25 as women have to pay lower premiums, since the statistics reflect that have a lower rate of accident due to his prudence.
Likewise, making use of the counts, the companies have come to the conclusion that the married people tend to have fewer accidents that the single drivers.
That is the use of the vehicle will influence the frequency, and with that in the probability of having any kind of mishap.
To increase the frequency increases the odds.
There are many variables that the insurance companies have in mind at the moment of establishing the price of the premium.
It is for that reason that the driver has to study the situation well to choose that certain of car that best suits their profile.
We will expose here the most significant variables at the moment to choose one or other type of insurance, so that this, in addition to being adapted to the characteristics of the insured, offers a reasonable price.
The young people under 25 years are with various objections to the time of hiring an insurance at a reasonable price, as are the limited experience in leadership and the antiquity of the card.
Although the ideal to be insured well is a sure, there are other economic options.
The most cautious drivers can opt for a whole risk with exemption, so that they obtain the coverage of an insurance to any risk but at a price more feasible.
This kind of agreement would mean that the customer pays a part of the amount of the accident.
"the hand of the amount of the catastrophe that contributes to the client will in terms of the value of the premium, that it will be higher the lower the amount", it specifies Luis Noguera, chief in Spain of first Europe, mediator insurance online.
The other option is an insurance extended to third parties, so that the customer is assured the protection in the face of damage caused to third parties, although not in the face of the caused in its own car.
In addition, it would be covered by theft, fire and the loss of the vehicle.
A Council.
If you are less than 25 years he tries to be careful and to prevent accidents as much as possible, since this will result in the advantage, being able to reduce the cost of insurance in the future.
A bonus is a reduction on the base rate that has the company.
On the contrary, a penalty is a surcharge on this base rate.
"the advantages and penalties will depend on the company and the benefit of this.
If the company has been a good year can be allowed to increase the advantages, "clarifies walnut tree.
The Gaza strip of the last 25 years, drivers have easier to hire insurance, since the index is reduced thanks to the accumulated experience.
For this reason, the more it is to use any risk with tax exemption.
"normally young people cannot make use of the experience previously acquired at the time of using in an accident, and even at the time of the leadership, it ensures the director in Spain of the European company, which adds that the majority of the accidents take place in the second year of conduct, once passed since the 'fear of novice.'
However, if the customer is married but do not yet have children is preferable to negotiate an insurance, provided their economic situation allows, of course.
For its part, the marriages with children are considered by the insurance companies and the public with smaller index, so that the extra charges will be lower.
In this case the best insurance would be one to any risk with exemption - being able to be this 300 Euros), or, when it had a high level of increase, one to third parties extended from the third year of the life of the vehicle.
"to carry out a more relaxed and have a greater purchasing power to afford the luxury of assuming a number of major exemption", sentences Luis walnut tree.
For the pensioners a certain to any risk with exemption (being this of 150 euro), or one to third-party insurance when they have a high level of increase.
It has to be said that the automobile insurance is something important, not only because it covers the driver in the face of possible accidents, but also because it represents an important cost, which is why it is fundamental to study adequately the sure that we need more according to our personal situation.
