Von receives in response to the negative criticism on the Olympic Games.
The Mayor of Hamburg received many criticisms of the politics and the economy does not ask for the Olympic Games of the summer.
Many people want to keep on fighting for the competitions in the section of aquatic sports.
But beust recalls that it is necessary to be realistic when considering the possibilities.
Hans-joerg schmidt-trenz, the Director General of the Chamber of Commerce in Hamburg, expressed on Wednesday this resignation as "no good for the economic location".
In the last time any other project in the big city encouraged so much motivation like the idea of the organization of the Olympic Games.
"without this objective would not be able to maintain the political momentum, sport at the same level.
Schmidt-trenz demanded at the Senate not to forget this project, but to find a new long-term application that refers to another time.
On Wednesday mayor smells von supported his statements that the ambitions of Hamburg in the organization of the Olympic Games to the summer is not carried out until at least 2028.
"Hamburg does not decide on the request for the Olympic Games, but that decides the German Federation of Olympic sports, says von in the Welt online.
He sent to the decision of the Federation of sport (sportbund) that is expected at the beginning of December, on the application of Munich for the Olympic Games the winter of 2028.
"this preference means for us that in this period of time, which up to now have until we thought 2028, from the point of view realistic will not have any opportunity".
In spite of everything, this dream did not put an end to always said von.
The Federation of sport of Hamburg (hsb) regrets the statements of von beut.
This gives the impression that in the next 25 years, Hamburg does not want to ask for the Olympic Games.
"It is too soon to remove the opportunity, if at this moment the plans are ruined," said the Wednesday Günter ploß, the director.
A renunciation of the request is contradictory to the declaration of the leader of the Senate, who made in a reception because of the general meeting of the German public Federation of sport to the high schools (adh).
There von designated the request from Hamburg to universiadas of 2015, not as a "substitution" of the Olympic Games in Hamburg.
Only last week the Federation of sport to the high schools named Hamburg as a candidate of the request.
