At that time, the request from Hamburg to the Olympic Games of the summer of 2012 caused a great enthusiasm.
But Hamburg failed because of Leipzig.
They are not the boxes of wood.
That relates to the terms Sweden and box of wood, thinks in Ikea, but do not think about Andy warhol.
Or does it?
At the moment the boxes of wood produced in Sweden are as the shadow that weighs on the list of works of warhol.
The greater part of the 1990s and brillo-box of "type" of this list are false.
After a few months ago the Swedish newspaper "expressen" put the question about the authenticity of shine-pits of 1968 of Andy warhol, the museum moderna of Stockholm carried out internal investigations, and came to conclusions: the six "shine-pits", that the museum hultén gave the museum moderna, are false, and almost a hundred of the other "type Stockholm", which are in circulation in the market of the international art, are also.
The prehistory is too complicated with a confused relationship between the artistic and patrocionadas productions.
In 1964 warhol created in New York, its first "shine-pits", painted the boxes, blue boxes of red and white, with the same shows that had soap powder of soap "shine."
In accordance with warhol, in the exposure of their works of 1968 in the museum moderna were exposed hundreds of cardboard. These did not warhol (because of the expenses), but which were brought directly from the factory box "shine."
It was not a question of works of art, but of units (which was only objects) exposed.
In the same year, 1968, warhol allowed to produce in Sweden of wood, but they were not exposed in the modern museet museum.
Witnesses of those times speak now that almost fifteen boxes, which at that time entered in the history of the art and the auction as original "brillo-boxes" to "type Stockholm" authorized by Andy warhol.
In auctions some of them were bought by more than 100 000 dollars.
The problem is that after the famous director of the museum hultén did false statements that in 1968 in Sweden were produced and exposed almost one hundred of the boxes of wood that warhol left it.
But in reality, 105 boxes were produced in the same year 1990 in Malmö for hultén and the exhibition in St. Petersburg.
In this time had already died from 3 years ago.
Lars byström, the leader of the Conservatives in the museum moderna, investigated six shine-pits property of Museum and three of the Swedish private property that was made in 1968 in Stockholm. First be printed and polished its tightened and later at the painted with the.
On the contrary, the structure of the copies of the 1990 shows that the painting was applied with a roller without printing directly the tight; in addition it is not a question of the oil painting, but that of the paint.
"these boxes have not been authorized by the artist and must be eliminated from the official list of shine-pits of Andy warhol", says Lars nittve, the director of the museum moderna and add that if the Commission of authentication "Andy warhol art" in New York did not come to any conclusion, the museum moderna classify these six boxes as copies / objects of exposure.
In July the Commission of authentication announced formally that accepts these "serious accusations" in that it is a question of boxes of soap dust.
But since that time there all remained in absolute silence.
The rebel soldiers surrender in Manila.
In the Philippines have given up the rebel soldiers who had taken refuge in a hotel in Manila, and had demanded the fall of the macapagal President Gloria Arroyo.
The Leader Antonio trillanes, who reproaches the President, corruption and electoral fraud, said a correspondent that could not respond to spill blood.
The soldiers faithful to the government had been assaulted the hotel using tear gas.
Almost two hundred soldiers were taking refuge for a few hours in the building.
Almost half of them, among them trillanes, had the Thursday trial for having tried to a coup d'état in the year 2003, which ended in failure.
It took advantage of the negotiations, suddenly to be able to settle with some 30 supporters.
Clearly the military police officers who had to watch it had gone to their ranks and followed its riot.
They entered in the hotel "Peninsula" and demanded the fall of the macapagal President Gloria Arroyo.
The troops of the government blocked the district in the vicinity of the hotel noble.
The President has called for an urgent meeting of the office of security.
Norberto Gonzales, the National Security Adviser, condemning the behaviour of the soldiers.
"the people is enough," said trillanes.
"We call on the people to go on to our ranks."
The general danilo Lim, that before managed the troops of elite scout reangers, said that soon other military troops wanted to follow the course.
The great critical of the government called on Thursday to a large demonstration against the President.
For months his government receives reproaches by corruption.
In 2003, the financial district in Manila was a place that attracted all the attention by the riot that was tried on stream.
The rise failed after nearly 24 hours by the army that it wanted to participate.
Since 1986 in the Philippines have had at least seven attempts of the State against the government elected democratically.
