Internet United guaranteed more than 20% of the actions of the business of versatel telecommunication.
On Wednesday the business reported that the average price for an action is 14, 46 euro.
It has only 20,05 per cent of the share capital.
There were many speculations about the absorption of the company.
There is also the options for increasing the financial part in versatel.
Internet United reported that with this step wants to accelerate the consolidation of the German market of dsl (line of digital subscriber).
On Wednesday already made the assumptions on the entry in the business, that the Bank has increased its participation in the user of network of duesseldorf by 5 by hundreds at 15.1 by hundreds.
In the financial market that means that the financial institution supports the titles of participation for a third Member.
Internet United in the previous day did participate with almost 10 per hundred to the business of telecommunication.
Drillisch in the measurement of capital increase placed 17.4 million new actions which have a value of 106.4 millions of euros.
United Internet has bought them millions of actions for 31.4 million euros.
In addition, the companies started with the negotiations on the cooperation of commercialization of the dsl-products.
"we strengthen our contribution", he told the potravoz of Internet united.
The two companies founded a joint company MSP, to acquire the competitive freenet.
On Thursday United Internet reported that at the beginning, the two companies want to be satisfied with the participation of ten per cent to freenet and not to make use of his right, that is to say, do take part 18,49 by hundreds of freenet.
That meant that both companies supported all the options, especially the participation in the corporation freenet.
The negotiations between Internet united and freenet on a strategic partnership ended in the middle of November.
This "play with freenet that will last for many months and it is not very understandable is part of the consolidation of the German market of telecom.
At the end of the third quarter freenet had 2.9 million customers with a contract of mobile telephone and 1.27 billion with a contract of dsl or a complete contract.
Until now, the holding of Internet united and drillisch had directly 6,01 per cent of the participation in freenet.
Then they had agreed that drillisch is going to achieve the other four per cent.
The right to buy 18.49 per cent of the society of investment was already agreed in August.
